            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I am proud to be a KJPS student ( batch 2014). Very good teaching style and I never relied on any tuitions which enabled me to score 92%. My sisters also studied in the same school and scored very well. We all participated in extra curriculars and had a good balance between studies and personal growth. Principal Anjali Ma'am and Dr. John provided immense support through out my studies. Teachers especially from 10th standard are very helpful and provided us extra classes to practice questions and for revising lessons.\nI always recommend KJPS.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
