            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "All other schools has completed syllabus of X std on priority, but this school didn't completed, they kept on focusing in rubbish such as annual days and other stuff.  The practice of annual days used to be near X std classroom,so students will not be able to focus bcos of noise. The syllabus of major subjects is incomplete till now and teachers are just finishing it for the sake of finishing without explaining anything in detail and giving the work to students to just finish notes from phone. There is one bhavna miss for physics, she showed video to students in a jiffy and just showed that her syllabus of physics is completed.  Like this teachers are trying to finish the syllabus anyhow and not even considering if students are understands it. There is no proper planning of lesson plans, teaching & schedule as in how to properly complete syllabus before time and make students understand concept. Teachers like bhawna miss and others are playing with future of students and principal Anjali madam is not paying any serious attention to it. Also they do not keep proper record of fees. Even when the fees is paid, they will not have a record of it. And will not give exam ticket to students.",
